'''Acibar''' neɣ '''Aluj''' ([[Assaɣ ussnan]]: '''Aloe''') d yiwet n [[tawsit (tudersent)|tawsit]] n [[imɣi uẓmam|tuẓmin]] yeṭṭafaren [[tawacult (tasnudert)|tawacult]] n [[timuwriɣin|tmuwriɣin]]. [[Talmest|Tilmas]] n tewsit-a d tid i d-yettemɣayen deg yineẓrufen d yidurar iɣuraren, ma d iẓuran-nsent seg tmura n Tferka n Unẓul am [[Namibya]] d [[Tafrikt n Wenẓul|Tferka n Unẓul]] akken daɣen i llant kra n telmas i d-yettemɣayen deg Tferka n Ugafa yakk d uneẓruf aserɣin.

== Asemres ==
Tilmas n tewsit-a d tid ilan (yesɛan) azal meqren deg ussuji n kra n waddaden d waṭṭanen am tirɣi acku issegmaw-d aglim yerɣan akken i yelha mgal n uɣelluy n ucebbub. 

